main event: A witness reported seeing 3 round white objects on 15.11.1965, which hovered near a field for about 15 to 20 minutes.
interesting points: The objects made a noise that was not like a helicopter,The objects moved suddenly and stopped,The witness described the objects as about 17 feet long,The witness indicated that the sighting was serious rather than imaginary,The objects ascended straight up and disappeared after the sighting.
witness description: a friend of the reporter, characterized as a reliable person
